---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="HD 85512 B -- Specialized Operations"
  description="HD 85512 B -- Class C specialized operations facility managed by Weyland-Yutani Corporation under government contract since 2042. Demonstrating operational excellence in corrections management."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center pt-20 pb-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          CLASS C -- SPECIALIZED OPERATIONS
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-[10rem] font-black text-white mb-4 leading-none uppercase">
          HD <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">85512 B</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-6"></div>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          SPECIALIZED OPERATIONS FACILITY
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Colony Data Bar -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 divide-x divide-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">LOCATION</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">HD 85512 B</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">SYSTEM</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">HD 85512</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">ESTABLISHED</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">2042</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">CLASSIFICATION</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">CLASS C -- SPECIALIZED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">STATUS</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] status-active">OPERATIONAL</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
            <div>
              <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
                FACILITY OVERVIEW
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8">
                OPERATIONAL <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">EXCELLENCE</span> IN EVERY ASSIGNMENT
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> HD 85512 B REPRESENTS WEYLAND-YUTANI'S COMMITMENT TO OPERATIONAL EXCELLENCE ACROSS THE FULL SPECTRUM OF COLONIAL ADMINISTRATION. ESTABLISHED IN 2042 UNDER A LONG-TERM CONTRACT WITH TERRESTRIAL AUTHORITIES, THE FACILITY OPERATES AS A GOVERNMENT-MANDATED CORRECTIONAL INSTALLATION MANAGED TO THE HIGHEST CORPORATE STANDARDS.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE INSTALLATION DEMONSTRATES THAT EVEN THE MOST CHALLENGING ADMINISTRATIVE ASSIGNMENTS BENEFIT FROM WEYLAND-YUTANI'S SYSTEMATIC APPROACH TO OPERATIONS MANAGEMENT. FACILITY DESIGN, STAFFING PROTOCOLS, SECURITY SYSTEMS, AND DAILY OPERATIONS ALL REFLECT DECADES OF INSTITUTIONAL EXPERTISE.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> HD 85512 B IS A MODEL OF CORRECTIONS MANAGEMENT IN THE INTERSTELLAR ERA. THE FACILITY'S REHABILITATION AND VOCATIONAL TRAINING PROGRAMS HAVE BEEN RECOGNIZED BY MULTIPLE OVERSIGHT BODIES AS EXAMPLES OF BEST PRACTICE IN OFF-WORLD CORRECTIONS ADMINISTRATION.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase border-b-2 border-[#FFC600] pb-3">FACILITY SPECIFICATIONS</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-mono">
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">DESIGNATION</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">HD 85512 B FACILITY</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">TYPE</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">CORRECTIONAL</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">ESTABLISHED</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">2042</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">CONTRACT</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">GOVERNMENT</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">CAPACITY</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FF0000] font-bold">RESTRICTED</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">STAFF COMPLEMENT</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FF0000] font-bold">RESTRICTED</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">SECURITY LEVEL</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">MAXIMUM</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">OVERSIGHT</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">ICC / W-Y JOINT</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Programs -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            PROGRAMS
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            REHABILITATION <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">& TRAINING</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">VT</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">VOCATIONAL TRAINING</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              COMPREHENSIVE SKILLS TRAINING PROGRAMS IN MECHANICAL SYSTEMS, ELECTRONIC REPAIR, CONSTRUCTION TRADES, AND AGRICULTURAL OPERATIONS. CERTIFICATIONS ARE RECOGNIZED ACROSS ALL W-Y COLONIAL OPERATIONS, PROVIDING PATHWAYS TO PRODUCTIVE POST-RELEASE EMPLOYMENT.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">BH</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">BEHAVIORAL HEALTH</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              STRUCTURED BEHAVIORAL HEALTH AND COUNSELING SERVICES ADDRESSING SUBSTANCE DEPENDENCY, ANGER MANAGEMENT, AND PSYCHOLOGICAL WELL-BEING. PROGRAMS ARE ADMINISTERED BY CERTIFIED CLINICAL STAFF IN ACCORDANCE WITH ICC CORRECTIONS STANDARDS.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">WP</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">WORK PROGRAMS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              STRUCTURED DAILY WORK ASSIGNMENTS PROVIDE ROUTINE, PURPOSE, AND PRACTICAL EXPERIENCE. ASSIGNMENTS ARE CALIBRATED TO INDIVIDUAL SKILL LEVELS AND ALIGNED WITH VOCATIONAL TRAINING GOALS. WORK CREDITS APPLY TOWARD SENTENCE REDUCTION.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">RE</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">REENTRY PREPARATION</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              PRE-RELEASE PROGRAMS PREPARE INDIVIDUALS FOR SUCCESSFUL REINTEGRATION INTO COLONIAL SOCIETY OR TERRESTRIAL RETURN. INCLUDES JOB PLACEMENT ASSISTANCE, HOUSING COORDINATION, AND ONGOING SUPPORT SERVICES THROUGH THE TRANSITION PERIOD.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Operational Standards -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              STANDARDS
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-4">
              OPERATIONAL <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">STANDARDS</span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">A+</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">ICC COMPLIANCE RATING</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">HIGHEST POSSIBLE RATING FROM THE INTERSTELLAR COMMERCE COMMISSION CORRECTIONS OVERSIGHT DIVISION.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">0</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">MAJOR INCIDENTS (5 YR)</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">ZERO MAJOR SECURITY INCIDENTS OVER THE PAST FIVE CONSECUTIVE REPORTING PERIODS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">72%</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">PROGRAM COMPLETION</div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs">VOCATIONAL AND REHABILITATION PROGRAM COMPLETION RATE, EXCEEDING THE INTERSTELLAR AVERAGE BY 23 POINTS.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="terminal mt-16">
            <div class="terminal-content">
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                &gt; "WEYLAND-YUTANI APPROACHES EVERY OPERATIONAL ASSIGNMENT WITH THE SAME COMMITMENT TO EXCELLENCE, WHETHER THE MISSION IS TERRAFORMING A NEW WORLD OR MANAGING A SPECIALIZED FACILITY UNDER GOVERNMENT CONTRACT. HD 85512 B DEMONSTRATES THAT CORPORATE PROFESSIONALISM AND SYSTEMATIC OPERATIONS MANAGEMENT PRODUCE SUPERIOR OUTCOMES IN ANY CONTEXT."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-l-4 border-[#FFC600] clip-corner">
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">NOTE:</span> CERTAIN FACILITY DETAILS, POPULATION FIGURES, AND OPERATIONAL SPECIFICS ARE RESTRICTED UNDER THE TERMS OF THE GOVERNMENT CONTRACT AND APPLICABLE ICC REGULATIONS. THIS PAGE PRESENTS PUBLICLY AVAILABLE INFORMATION ONLY. AUTHORIZED OVERSIGHT PERSONNEL MAY REQUEST DETAILED FACILITY REPORTS THROUGH ESTABLISHED CHANNELS.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <section class="relative py-12 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/colonies" class="btn-secondary">ALL COLONIES</a>
          <a href="/colonies/fiorina-161" class="btn-secondary">FIORINA 161</a>
          <a href="/careers" class="btn-primary">STAFF OPPORTUNITIES</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
